# dwm installation

pacman -S xorg-server xorg-init xorg-randr xorg-xsetroot nitrogen picom 
clone, make clean install from official git repos of dwm, dmenu, st
cp /etc/X11/xinitrc ~/.xinitrc
remove last 4-5 lines from .xinitrc and replace with 'exec dwm' (refer xinitrc in repository)
use 'startx' command to start display server, or include startx command in .bash_profile or .bashrc
